[Site ""]
[Date ""]
[Board "2"]
[Dealer "N"]
[Vulnerable "NS"]
[Deal "N:A7.J85.AQ74.T754 QJT93.KQ4.863.82 65.T762.KJ92.AJ6 K842.A93.T5.KQ93"]
[Declarer "E"]
[Contract "3S"]
[Result ""]
[Auction "N"]
1D 1S pass 3S pass pass pass
[BCFlags "1f"]
[RotationNote "Board 2, chOption: E, chBasis: S, basisKind:Declarer, nOption:1, nBasis: 2, nRot: 3, useStandardVul: true"]
[VersionToken "0de83636920e1fbd3efcebafdd6e44abdb7ed7eba75480cf831c110619ad143d"]
[Category "Competitive Bidding"]
[Difficulty "beginner"]
[SkillPath "competitive_bidding/overcalls"]
[Student "S"]
{The bidding has been as shown.  

You have enough for a 1-level Overcall so you bid 1\S. Partner says 3\S.  

The jump raise tells you partner has 11-14 points.

With your minimum it's going to have to be better than that to get you excited. So you pass.}

[Event ""]
[Site ""]
[Date ""]
