[VersionToken "7a72c996745c41fa5018f13fcc19df259c010309a3793e65b3abc0f03689d5a8"]
[Category "Competitive Bidding"]
[Difficulty "beginner"]
[SkillPath "competitive_bidding/overcalls"]
[Student "S"]
{The bidding has been as shown.   

You have 10 points, but in cases like this points don't matter that much. They <b>MIGHT</b> be able to make 4\H. Partner <b>MIGHT</b> be able to make 4\S. This preemptive jump takes the decision away from them.

Looking at the hands you can see that partner is going to go down 1 at 4\S. However, that is an excellent result since they appear to be cold for 5\H.}

